item.dc:creator: @deathschaos9 DeathsChaos9
item.description:
@deathschaos9 wrote:

A return statement will be one of the following.

break; // With or without label
return; // With or without value
throw; // With label only. Ex. throw IOException();
continue; //With or without label

A { is not a return statement.
